    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0806b09"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>京師章信寺<persName key="A011293">道澄</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0806b10"/><persName key="A011293">釋道澄</persName>，姓梁氏，<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>人也。父<persName key="A019402">涉</persName>中書舍人。生<lb
ed="T" n="0806b11"/>而奇表，輒惡葷肴，出家如歸，無所顧戀。忽<lb
ed="T" n="0806b12"/>遇禪僧，摩頂與立名曰<persName key="A011293">道澄</persName>，缾錫常隨，冥<lb
ed="T" n="0806b13"/>合律範，號律沙彌也。受具之後，習聽《南山<lb
ed="T" n="0806b14"/>律》於諸學處，微其玷缺。然性都率略，住寺不<lb
ed="T" n="0806b15"/>恒，或<placeName key="PL000000042297">奉恩</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042412">莊嚴</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042657">草堂</placeName>等寺，所到便居，護生為<lb
ed="T" n="0806b16"/>切。<date from-iso="0781-02-02" key="j20063472006701" to-iso="0782-01-22">建中二年</date>，坐夏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g61"/>於雲陽山<!--找不到此地-->，有虎哮吼入<lb
ed="T" n="0806b17"/>其門。<persName key="A011293">澄</persName>徐語之，其虎搖尾襵耳而退。徙居<lb
ed="T" n="0806b18"/><placeName key="PL000000042180">章信寺</placeName>，或問其故，<persName key="A011293">澄</persName>曰：「出家者可滯一方<lb
ed="T" n="0806b19"/>乎？<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>三時分房，俾無貪著，觀門易立矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0806b20"/>不然者，豈通方廣恕乎？」<date key="j20082152008215" when-iso="0786-03-16">貞元二年二月八日</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0806b21"/><persName key="A004215">帝</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042180">寺</placeName>受菩薩戒，京甸傾瞻，賜齎隆洽，所<lb
ed="T" n="0806b22"/>受而迴施二田矣。<date from-iso="0789-02-04" key="j20092712009624" to-iso="0790-01-23">五年</date>，<persName key="A004215">帝</persName>幸其<placeName key="PL000000042180">寺</placeName>，問<persName key="A011293">澄</persName>修<lb
ed="T" n="0806b23"/>心法門。又勅為妃主嬪御受菩薩戒。<date from-iso="0800-05-02" key="j20133762013404" to-iso="0800-05-30">十六<lb
ed="T" n="0806b24"/>年四月</date>，勅賜號曰<persName key="A011293">大圓</persName>。<date key="j20146332014633" when-iso="0803-10-11">十九年九月十八<lb
ed="T" n="0806b25"/>日</date>，終于此<placeName key="PL000000042180">寺</placeName>焉。</p>
